metadata.name: Cube
metadata.description:
This artwork was created when the pandemic started. Then I was all alone, in a city where a hard lockdown was introduced. I felt cut off from the whole world, and knowing that there is so much life around, I was forced to stay in my "glass cube".

The cube is a protection against external threats, but at the same time it is a destroyer of the internal supports.
